Package view

package view
  • Class
    Description
    AddNumberView
    The AddNumberView class implements the code to add the text field, and the button to add the number Calls the AddNumber controller when the button is clicked.
    BasicStatsView
    The BasicStatsView class is the Composite class of View.
    CountView
    The CountView class implements the logic to add and display the count field, and compute the count.
    MaxView
    The MaxView class implements the logic to add and display the max field, and compute the max value.
    MeanView
    The MeanView class implements the logic to add and display the mean field, and compute the mean.
    MedianView
    The MedianView class implements the logic to add and display the median field, and compute the median.
    NumbersView
    The NumbersView class implements the logic to update and display the list of numbers.
    ResetView
    The ResetView class implements the logic to add the reset button, and call the reset controller when the button is clicked.
    SimpleStatisticView
    Strategy Design pattern applied with the different helper classes for respective statistics.
    SimpleStatisticView.ComputeStrategy
    Interface to compute the appropriate simple statistic.
    SimpleStatisticView.CountStatistic
    Count of numbers added so far.
    SimpleStatisticView.MaxStatistic
    Compute the maximum of an array of numbers.
    SimpleStatisticView.MeanStatistic
    Compute the mean of an array of numbers.
    SimpleStatisticView.MedianStatistic
    Compute the median of an array of numbers.
    UndoView
    The UndoView class implements the logic to add the undo button, and call the undo controller when the button is clicked.
    View
    The View interface represents a visualization of the BasicStatsModel.
    ViewUtils
    The ViewUtils class contains all the logic for the math we do on the numbers added.
